<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-5431] cassandra-shuffle with JMX usernames and passwords</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-5431</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Unlike nodetool, cassandra-shuffle doesn&apos;t allow passing in a JMX username and password. This stops those who want to switch to vnodes from doing so if JMX access requires a username and a password.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Patch to follow.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
